{"tid":1589811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和理shop行動","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:28:38.000Z","uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e8ec95f98f3eb92aff03164ad4e96a2aee56bf","tid":1589811,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"以後和理shop希望只會係以人數,係商場入面塞爆人,令顧客唔方便,放棄入去,或者甚至係好難以入去,又或者齋睇唔買<br />\n而唔係直接去影響商鋪,直接去打爛或者去影響佢地員工<br />\n咁樣一黎狗真係唔會直接入去,琴日都已經見到,班狗無接報係唔撚敢入商場<br />\n因為商場會知如果俾狗入去,佢幾日唔洗做生意<br />\n要揸住呢張牌黎玩<br />\n真係希望和理shop係真正既完全和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求,缺一不可"},{"pid":"b4c0a554060cf4c6f449397ed8759a7b7b7506cb","tid":1589811,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d50bd1f414b848bebdee0a1eb0c9e1bbdc6cb7d2","tid":1589811,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa118f9cd9613ba1c4bb04806e364e82a1792de","tid":1589811,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0b053912f5f1b4dcfdcdb4e3a53cff660d2af3f","tid":1589811,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"同埋要係入面做乜都好,最緊要爽手同埋唔好俾鏡頭影到<br />\n鏡頭一到即止就岩<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位"},{"pid":"ceb0ed7290c5eef0d9a3c89967dc0f24ed66bcf0","tid":1589811,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"7b612fe6e0b228a631e7a29eb7ba9b8a2e2e5273","tid":1589811,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5eb59a168720033ba2f23e5a6f687f47b58